## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| plink2_common.cc pulls in too many dependencies | Build fails | Audit includes, stub unused functions |
| BigStack allocator required | Runtime crash | Initialize bigstack in bind or replace with aligned_malloc |
| GlmLinear file I/O too entangled | Can't extract results | Fall back to per-variant compute extraction |
| plink2_thread.h conflicts with DuckDB threading | Deadlocks | Use single-threaded compute in Phase 1 |
| NOLAPACK SVD too slow for many covariates | Performance | Add optional BLAS/LAPACK in Phase 3 |
| Symbol conflicts between plink2_common and our plink_common | Link errors | Different namespaces (plink2:: vs duckdb::) |

