## Performance Targets

| Dataset | plink2 --glm | plink_glm target | SQL baseline |
|---------|-------------|-----------------|-------------|
| 4 var × 4 samp | <1ms | <10ms | <10ms |
| 3K var × 8 samp | ~5ms | <50ms | ~100ms |
| 30K var × 10K samp | 61ms | <200ms | 1.8s |
| 300K var × 500K samp | ~seconds | ~10s | infeasible |

Phase 1 target: within 3× of plink2 for the NOLAPACK path.
BLAS/LAPACK support (Phase 3) should close the remaining gap.
